<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Plessey to quit consumer products business.</title>
<headline>Plessey to quit consumer products business.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-04-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Plessey Corp Ltd said on Monday it had reached an agreement with Omega Holdings Ltd whereby Plessey will dispose of its remaining interests in consumer products.</p>
<p>Last month Omega acquired Plessey's operations relating to marketing and distribution of Telefunken and Pioneer products in South Africa.</p>
<p>A further announcemnt will be made in due course, Plessey said.</p>
